	<h1 class="title">这里有份解读80、90、95后的报告，你怎么看？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3926/small/3926.jpg?1421980719" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">费丽婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-15 11:04:44 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23875/medium/23875.jpg?1457965809" alt="" />			
	</div>
